##Ministry of Civil Affairs Responds to "fake Wuhan residential area" incident

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

This is a roundup for the paper

The joint prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council held a press conference on March 9.

In response to the "fake practice" in the Kaiyuan Mansion community, Cuiyuan community, Qingshan district, Wuhan, Chen Yueliang, director of the Department of grass-roots political power construction and community governance of the Ministry of Civil Affairs, said that, this has seriously harmed the "body" of the organization and the image of the Party and the government.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Previously reported

On the morning of March 5, during a visit by the central guidance team to the Kaiyuan Mansion community in Cuiyuan community, Qingshan district, Wuhan, some residents shouted from their windows: "fake, fake. " Reflect the community property pretend to let volunteers send meat and vegetables to the owners, the actual work is not in place, causing widespread concern throughout society.

Previously reported "Wuhan residents shouted "false" , the central guidance group moved the real case" , can view details of the stamp map

The paper reviews

This is a very meaningful expression of public opinion and Response to public opinion. The central guidance team went to the front line to investigate in order to understand the real situation and solve the real problems. Fraud was both a distraction to the public and a distraction from the work of the Steering Group, and fortunately there was that loud and clear cry from instinct, which betrayed everything.

Epidemic situation is a mirror, all people, all things clearly, really not false, false really not. From the beginning of the epidemic to the present, from Wuhan, Hubei to the country, each link in each job to do, the public has always known. For those who sacrifice dedication, people have never been stingy praise, for those who make trouble, people will be directly exposed and vilified. In the end, all it takes is to get back to the Seek truth from facts.
